---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import DateDifferenceCalculator from '../../components/tools/DateDifferenceCalculator';

const title = "Free Date Difference Calculator - Calculate Days Between Dates | Utility Hub";
const description = "Calculate the exact number of days, weeks, months, and years between two dates. Free online date difference calculator with weekday and weekend breakdown.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical="/tools/date-difference-calculator">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 py-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Date Difference Calculator</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Calculate the exact difference between any two dates. Get results in days, weeks, months, years, plus a breakdown of weekdays and weekends.</p>
      <DateDifferenceCalculator client:load />
      <article class="prose prose-gray max-w-none mt-12">
        <h2>What is a Date Difference Calculator?</h2>
        <p>A date difference calculator is a free online tool that calculates the exact duration between two dates. It provides results in multiple time units including total days, weeks, months, and years, plus a breakdown of how many weekdays and weekends fall between the dates.</p>
        <h2>How to Use This Date Difference Calculator</h2>
        <p>Simply select a start date and an end date using the date pickers, then click "Calculate Difference." The calculator instantly shows the total days, weeks, months, years, weekdays, and weekends between the two dates.</p>
        <h2>Use Cases</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Project planning:</strong> Calculate project duration and deadlines</li>
          <li><strong>Event planning:</strong> Count days until an event or since an event</li>
          <li><strong>Employment:</strong> Calculate employment tenure and service periods</li>
          <li><strong>Legal deadlines:</strong> Track court dates and filing deadlines</li>
          <li><strong>Personal milestones:</strong> Count days since a wedding, anniversary, or other milestone</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Internal Links</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/tools/age-calculator">Age Calculator</a> - Calculate exact age</li>
          <li><a href="/tools/timestamp-converter">Timestamp Converter</a> - Convert timestamps to dates</li>
          <li><a href="/tools/percentage-calculator">Percentage Calculator</a> - Calculate percentages</li>
          <li><a href="/tools/compound-interest-calculator">Compound Interest Calculator</a> - Investment growth</li>
          <li><a href="/tools/bmi-calculator">BMI Calculator</a> - Check your BMI</li>
        </ul>
        <h4>Frequently Asked Questions</h4>
        <p>Question: Does this include both start and end dates? Answer: Yes, the calculation includes both dates in the total count.</p>
        <p>Question: Is this tool accurate for leap years? Answer: Yes, our calculator accounts for leap years automatically.</p>
        <p>Question: Can I calculate business days? Answer: Yes, the tool provides a breakdown of weekdays and weekends.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
</write_to_file>